{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:1","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.001.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. Ja 1:21. (\u00c9p 2:20-22. Ac 4:11, 12.) (\u00c9s 28:16. Mt 21:42-44. Ro 9:30-33.) Ap 1:6. Ro 9:24-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Rejetant donc toute malice et toute ruse, la dissimulation, l\u2019envie, et toute m\u00e9disance,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2","name":"1 Pierre 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25","name":"1 Pierre 1:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.1.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:2","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>d\u00e9sirez, comme des enfants nouveau-n\u00e9s, le lait spirituel et pur, afin que par lui vous croissiez pour le salut,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3","name":"1 Pierre 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1","name":"1 Pierre 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:3","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>si vous avez go\u00fbt\u00e9 que le Seigneur est bon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4","name":"1 Pierre 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2","name":"1 Pierre 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:4","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Approchez-vous de lui, pierre vivante, rejet\u00e9e par les hommes, mais choisie et pr\u00e9cieuse devant Dieu;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5","name":"1 Pierre 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3","name":"1 Pierre 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:5","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>et vous-m\u00eames, comme des pierres vivantes, \u00e9difiez-vous pour former une maison spirituelle, un saint sacerdoce, afin d\u2019offrir des victimes spirituelles, agr\u00e9ables \u00e0 Dieu par J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6","name":"1 Pierre 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4","name":"1 Pierre 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:6","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Car il est dit dans l\u2019\u00c9criture:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Voici, je mets en Sion une pierre angulaire, choisie, pr\u00e9cieuse;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">et celui qui croit en elle ne sera point confus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7","name":"1 Pierre 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5","name":"1 Pierre 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:7","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u2019honneur est donc pour vous, qui croyez. Mais, pour les incr\u00e9dules,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    La pierre qu\u2019ont rejet\u00e9e ceux qui b\u00e2tissaient<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Est devenue la principale de l\u2019angle,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et une pierre d\u2019achoppement<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et un rocher de scandale;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8","name":"1 Pierre 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6","name":"1 Pierre 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:8","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>ils s\u2019y heurtent pour n\u2019avoir pas cru \u00e0 la parole, et c\u2019est \u00e0 cela qu\u2019ils sont destin\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9","name":"1 Pierre 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7","name":"1 Pierre 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:9","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Vous, au contraire, vous \u00eates une race \u00e9lue, un sacerdoce royal, une nation sainte, un peuple acquis, afin que vous annonciez les vertus de celui qui vous a appel\u00e9s des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres \u00e0 son admirable lumi\u00e8re,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10","name":"1 Pierre 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8","name":"1 Pierre 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:10","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>vous qui autrefois n\u2019\u00e9tiez pas un peuple, et qui maintenant \u00eates le peuple de Dieu, vous qui n\u2019aviez pas obtenu mis\u00e9ricorde, et qui maintenant avez obtenu mis\u00e9ricorde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11","name":"1 Pierre 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9","name":"1 Pierre 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:11","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortations diverses: la bonne conduite au milieu des pa\u00efens, la soumission aux autorit\u00e9s, les devoirs des serviteurs, les devoirs des femmes et des maris, le support et la paix, la patience dans les \u00e9preuves<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-17: cf. (\u00c9p 4:1. Mt 5:11, 16.) Ro 13:1-8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Bien-aim\u00e9s, je vous exhorte, comme \u00e9trangers et voyageurs sur la terre, \u00e0 vous abstenir des convoitises charnelles qui font la guerre \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12","name":"1 Pierre 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10","name":"1 Pierre 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:12","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ayez au milieu des pa\u00efens une bonne conduite, afin que, l\u00e0 m\u00eame o\u00f9 ils vous calomnient comme si vous \u00e9tiez des malfaiteurs, ils remarquent vos bonnes \u0153uvres, et glorifient Dieu, au jour o\u00f9 il les visitera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13","name":"1 Pierre 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11","name":"1 Pierre 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:13","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Soyez soumis, \u00e0 cause du Seigneur, \u00e0 toute autorit\u00e9 \u00e9tablie parmi les hommes, soit au roi comme souverain,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14","name":"1 Pierre 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12","name":"1 Pierre 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:14","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>soit aux gouverneurs comme envoy\u00e9s par lui pour punir les malfaiteurs et pour approuver les gens de bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15","name":"1 Pierre 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13","name":"1 Pierre 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:15","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Car c\u2019est la volont\u00e9 de Dieu qu\u2019en pratiquant le bien vous r\u00e9duisiez au silence les hommes ignorants et insens\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16","name":"1 Pierre 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14","name":"1 Pierre 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:16","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\u00e9tant libres, sans faire de la libert\u00e9 un voile qui couvre la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, mais agissant comme des serviteurs de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17","name":"1 Pierre 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15","name":"1 Pierre 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:17","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Honorez tout le monde; aimez les fr\u00e8res; craignez Dieu; honorez le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18","name":"1 Pierre 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16","name":"1 Pierre 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:18","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.019,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 18-25: cf. (\u00c9p 6:5-8. Tit 2:9, 10.) (1 Pi 3:14-18. \u00c9s 53:3-12. Mt 16:24.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\n    Serviteurs, soyez soumis en toute crainte \u00e0 vos ma\u00eetres, non seulement \u00e0 ceux qui sont bons et doux, mais aussi \u00e0 ceux qui sont d\u2019un caract\u00e8re difficile.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19","name":"1 Pierre 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17","name":"1 Pierre 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:19","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Car c\u2019est une gr\u00e2ce que de supporter des afflictions par motif de conscience envers Dieu, quand on souffre injustement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20","name":"1 Pierre 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18","name":"1 Pierre 2:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:20","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>En effet, quelle gloire y a-t-il \u00e0 supporter de mauvais traitements pour avoir commis des fautes? Mais si vous supportez la souffrance lorsque vous faites ce qui est bien, c\u2019est une gr\u00e2ce devant Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21","name":"1 Pierre 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19","name":"1 Pierre 2:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:21","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et c\u2019est \u00e0 cela que vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9s, parce que Christ aussi a souffert pour vous, vous laissant un exemple, afin que vous suiviez ses traces,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22","name":"1 Pierre 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20","name":"1 Pierre 2:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:22","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Lui qui n\u2019a point commis de p\u00e9ch\u00e9, et dans la bouche duquel il ne s\u2019est point trouv\u00e9 de fraude;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23","name":"1 Pierre 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21","name":"1 Pierre 2:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:23","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>lui qui, injuri\u00e9, ne rendait point d\u2019injures, maltrait\u00e9, ne faisait point de menaces, mais s\u2019en remettait \u00e0 celui qui juge justement;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24","name":"1 Pierre 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22","name":"1 Pierre 2:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:24","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.002.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>lui qui a port\u00e9 lui-m\u00eame nos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s en son corps sur le bois, afin que morts aux p\u00e9ch\u00e9s nous vivions pour la justice; lui par les meurtrissures duquel vous avez \u00e9t\u00e9 gu\u00e9ris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25","name":"1 Pierre 2:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23","name":"1 Pierre 2:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.25","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 2:25","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.002.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.2.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Car vous \u00e9tiez comme des brebis errantes. Mais maintenant vous \u00eates retourn\u00e9s vers le pasteur et le gardien de vos \u00e2mes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2","name":"1 Pierre 2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1","name":"1 Pierre 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24","name":"1 Pierre 2:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.2.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb8386216.97324660');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8386216.97324660\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb8386216.97324660","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb8386216.97324660'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb8386216.97324660\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}